<p>Attached please find written comments from Dr. John K. Holton, Director of the Illinois Department on Aging, supporting the role of the Aging Network in the National Alzheimer's Plan and the importance of addressing the needs of caregivers of persons with dementia.</p>
<p>Please contact me should you have any questions.</p>
