<p>The Center for Excellence in Assisted Living (CEAL) appreciates the opportunity to comment on the draft framework for the National Plan to Address Alzheimer's Disease. Our comments are attached in Microsoft Word and Adobe Acrobat formats. Feel free to contact me if you have any questions or wish to discuss the comments.</p>
